  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Changing a Security Transaction</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loiod818da531198434de10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Changing a Security Transaction </h1><div class=\"body\">\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"> You can use this function to change the current data of a security transaction if the transaction flows still have the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Blocked for posting</span> status <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">.</span> When you have made your changes, the security transaction stays in the activity as before.\n</p>\n<aside class=\"note sap-example example\" aria-labelledby=\"n0t\"><div class=\"title\" id=\"n0t\"><strong>Example</strong></div>\n<p class=\"p\"> If the current activity of the transaction you want to change is <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">order</span> , you can only transfer it to the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">contract</span> activity using the <a class=\"xref\" href=\"f018da531198434de10000000a174cb4.html\">Executing a Security Order</a> function.\n</p></aside>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Procedure\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Procedure</h2>\n<ol class=\"ol\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Trading</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Transaction</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">ChangeorBack office</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Transaction</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Change .</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span>\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Enter the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Company code</span> and the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Transaction number</span> of the transaction you want to change.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Choose <img class=\"inline\" src=\"loio0249e0530920444de10000000a174cb4_LowRes.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"> (ENTER).\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Enter the data you want to change.\n</p><p class=\"p\"> - <span class=\"ph\">Structure</span>\n</p><p class=\"p\"> - <span class=\"ph\">Administration</span>\n</p><p class=\"p\"> - <span class=\"ph\">Trading Data</span>\n</p><p class=\"p\"> - <span class=\"ph\">Editing Other Flows for the Transaction</span>\n</p><p class=\"p\"> - <span class=\"ph\">Payment Details</span>\n</p><p class=\"p\"> - <span class=\"ph\">Cash Flow for the Transaction</span>\n</p><p class=\"p\"> - <span class=\"ph\">Memos</span>\n</p><p class=\"p\"> - <span class=\"ph\">Status</span>\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Choose <img class=\"inline\" src=\"loio7be6df53e957444de10000000a174cb4_LowRes.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Position cash flows</span> (in the upper part of the screen) to display the cash flows for the securities account, including the transaction currently being processed. <span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">See also</span> : <a class=\"xref\" href=\"2d18da531198434de10000000a174cb4.html\">Cash Flow</a>\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><img class=\"inline\" src=\"loiocfd9df53e957444de10000000a174cb4_LowRes.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"> Save your entries.\n</p></li></ol>\n</section></div>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
}